{"tid":2323950,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"5444 8158 香港人no show 文化","createTime":"2020-12-13T14:28:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-13T14:49:37.000Z","uid":186852,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"6b3c19f4d72053a524e56a7d6641be665c2137b4","tid":2323950,"uid":186852,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T14:28:43.000Z","msg":"本來今日晏晝1點約左人交收波鞋，條友今朝9點仲覆陣間見，我出門前仲wts左佢講我出發去緊交收地點，但係藍tick左我，到左最後居然可以block 左我仲no show。唔買唔緊要，出聲咪得囉，點解要我山長水遠出左黎之後no show。我真係嬲到要放佢電話出黎，想警惕其他人唔好賣野比佢之餘，仲想唱衰佢，唔好助長佢哩種no show 文化。<br />\n<br />\n其實香港時下年青人都覺得唔守時，要對方等係理所當然，有啲直情講黎緊，但係最後都可以講唔黎。到底一開始講&ldquo;黎緊&ldquo;係咪講緊大話，點解會突然出左黎又變左唔黎。哩種無責任感嘅no show風氣真係非常惡劣，亦都反映講大話同無責任感嘅低等人格。<br />\n<br />\n電話 5444 8158<br />\nfd：<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8nqzgqw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8nqzgqw.png&h=95ada750&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n歡迎夜晚打比佢提醒佢唔好再有啲咁低等嘅行為。"},{"pid":"108d4ef006e49e10822010c86bf71d69c7183f8f","tid":2323950,"uid":38970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T14:29:53.000Z","msg":"無聊"},{"pid":"0fe5e35502bad40fc59977381011b071e880fe87","tid":2323950,"uid":14131,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T14:30:38.000Z","msg":"睇黎樓主係真係22歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aecf0977872821993bc8ee238af40f892e38d6a5","tid":2323950,"uid":89517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T14:31:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e384ebcb2a8a9b40791ae200d8e28af7721d4e85","tid":2323950,"uid":89337,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T14:40:16.000Z","msg":"仲以為睇緊fb group d棄單post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />